<br>
Thwacked with the nerf stick.<br>
<br>
Yeah, it might be intended for the lower levels of fletching, but even those weren't cheap... even plat to my name and the assistance of others has gone into fletching... for 39 levels.  I could have gotten higher faster with more plat, but... well... I didn't have the plat.<br>
<br>
Sorry... jsut needed to rant.<br>
<br>
-Caillou Kyrielle<br>
Bippin's betrothed<br>
Fletching at 208<br>
